3. IF THE TWO SECTIONS EVER CONFLICT
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For a given file, the more specific statement wins: a `_license` header inside a
fixture governs that fixture; otherwise section 1 governs the paths it lists and
section 2 governs everything else.
